<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Perfil de Usuario</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <%- include('partials/navigation')%>
    </header>
    
    <div class="container mt-4">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" class="rounded-circle mb-3" alt="John Doe">
                        <h3>John Doe</h3>
                        <p>Full Stack Developer</p>
                    
                        
                        <hr>
                        <div class="text-start">
                            <p><i class="material-icons align-middle">person</i> Biografía:</p>
                            <p>¡Hola! Soy un apasionado desarrollador web y diseñador creativo. Me encanta crear experiencias digitales únicas y atractivas. Siempre estoy aprendiendo nuevas tecnologías y explorando formas innovadoras de resolver problemas.</p>
                            <p><i class="material-icons align-middle">language</i> <a href="https://bootdey.com">https://bootdey.com</a></p>
                            <p><i class="material-icons align-middle">code</i> <a href="#">bootdey</a></p>
                            <p><i class="material-icons align-middle">share</i> <a href="#">@bootdey</a></p>
                            <p><i class="material-icons align-middle">camera_alt</i> <a href="#">bootdey</a></p>
                            <p><i class="material-icons align-middle">facebook</i> <a href="#">bootdey</a></p>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <div class="card mb-4">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Información de perfil</h5>
                        <form>
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label for="firstName" class="form-label">Nombres</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="firstName" value="John">
                            </div>
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label for="lastName" class="form-label">Apellidos</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="lastName" value="Doe">
                            </div>
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label for="email" class="form-label">Correo Electrónico</label>
                                <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" value="john@example.com">
                            </div>
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label for="biography" class="form-label">Biografía</label>
                                <textarea class="form-control" id="biography" rows="4"></textarea>
                            </div>
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Guardar cambios</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Progreso de Cursos</h5>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label class="form-label">HTML</label>
                            <div class="progress">
                                <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" style="width: 100%; background-color: darkorange;" aria-valuenow="100" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label class="form-label">TypeScript</label>
                            <div class="progress">
                                <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" style="width: 100%; background-color:rgb(17, 34, 144)" aria-valuenow="100" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label class="form-label">JavaScript</label>
                            <div class="progress">
                                <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" style="width: 100%; background-color: gold;" aria-valuenow="100" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label class="form-label">CSS</label>
                            <div class="progress">
                                <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" style="width: 75%;background-color: blue;" aria-valuenow="75" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label class="form-label">Python</label>
                            <div class="progress">
                                <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" style="width: 100%; background-color: #add8e6;" aria-valuenow="100" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>